%% --- SIPARIS DURUM ---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft: Sepete eklendi

    Draft --> PendingPayment: Siparis ver
    PendingPayment --> PaymentProcessing: Odeme basladi

    PaymentProcessing --> Confirmed: Odeme basarili
    PaymentProcessing --> PaymentFailed: Odeme basarisiz

    PaymentFailed --> PendingPayment: Tekrar dene
    PaymentFailed --> Cancelled: Iptal

    Confirmed --> Preparing: Hazirlaniyor
    Confirmed --> Cancelled: Musteri iptal (iade)

    Preparing --> Shipped: Kargoya verildi
    Shipped --> Delivered: Teslim edildi
    Shipped --> ReturnRequested: Iade talebi

    Delivered --> ReturnRequested: Iade talebi (7 gun)
    Delivered --> Completed: Sure doldu (7 gun)

    ReturnRequested --> ReturnApproved: Iade onaylandi
    ReturnRequested --> ReturnRejected: Iade reddedildi
    ReturnApproved --> Refunded: Para iade edildi

    Cancelled --> [*]
    Completed --> [*]
    Refunded --> [*]
    ReturnRejected --> Completed
